---
title: Roasted Chicken and Cheese Flautas with Crema and Spinach Salad
description: These flautas are a double whammy! We can’t decide what we like more, the tangy crema or the incredible creamy Mexican-spiced chicken! Luckily, both flavours are present in these baked tortillas. Enjoy!
